  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_3_516-601",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "516-601",
      "markText": "在乡村，在田野，你不会丢失任何东西。即使你丢失了什么东西，到头来你也会发现，你其实什么都没有丢失。那些你不慎丢失了的，有的被其他生灵借用，有的被时间收藏，有的被土地认养。",
      "totalCount": 590,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=516&rangeEnd=601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=516&rangeEnd=601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_3_1089-1173",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1089-1173",
      "markText": "你知道它们是不结穗子和豆子的，它们短暂的、站在高处的一生，是一阵风导致的美丽错误。它们索性在这些短暂的日子里，认真地打出绿色的手语，把美丽的错误，变成纯粹的风景和美丽。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1089&rangeEnd=1173",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1089&rangeEnd=1173"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_3_846-942",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "846-942",
      "markText": "你丢失的那根柳木拐杖，是你在走亲戚的路上歇息时顺手插在溪边的，你落在了那里。几天后，当你返回，柳木拐杖已经发芽，过些年就会长成一棵大柳树。无意中，你在土地上留下一个多么葱茏的念想和美好的签名。",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=846&rangeEnd=942",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=846&rangeEnd=942"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_7_672-716",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "672-716",
      "markText": "小时候，每年过庙，村里都会请戏班子来唱戏，这对孩子们来说，是比过年还要盛大和欢欣的节日。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=716",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=716"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_11_3580-3600",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3580-3600",
      "markText": "寒冷、静谧和孤独是当代世界的三样奢侈品。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3580&rangeEnd=3600",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3580&rangeEnd=3600"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_9_7481-7532",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "7481-7532",
      "markText": "“警方悬赏五十美元，给逮到逃犯的人。通风报信让警方逮到逃犯，只给二十五美元。我想那条裙子都快想疯了。”",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7481&rangeEnd=7532",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7481&rangeEnd=7532"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_7_3159-3189",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3159-3189",
      "markText": "几年后，我离开了那个镇子，从此再也没有见过那些庙会上的歌者。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3159&rangeEnd=3189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3159&rangeEnd=3189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_5_1732-1829",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1732-1829",
      "markText": "心无旁骛很重要，你一心一意去感受那些块面、那些线条，刻莲花时能闻到莲香，刻小虫时能感受到触须的弹动，能感受到秋虫的喜怒哀乐。你沉浸其中，就会忘了手上的刻刀有千钧重，忘了咽口水，你就逐渐上道了。”",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1732&rangeEnd=1829",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1732&rangeEnd=1829"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_3_442-455",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "442-455",
      "markText": "在田野，你不会丢失任何东西",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=455",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=455"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_16_2374-2427",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2374-2427",
      "markText": "“我们最后变成什么样，并不取决于我们选择了哪条道路，而是取决于我们的内心。”无论如何，都要保持我们的内心。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2374&rangeEnd=2427",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2374&rangeEnd=2427"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300047636_11_6291-6311",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6291-6311",
      "markText": "森林里是有正义的。但往往不是人类的正义。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300047636&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6291&rangeEnd=6311",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90332f00813ab791bg01662d?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6291&rangeEnd=6311"
